 eur  in bridge loans during the period  most lenders of bridge loans covering over  of the value of bridge loans have agreed to extend their bridge loans to expire on  february  and to reduce the interest rates   as part of the agreement a total of eur  of receivables under the bridge loans have been converted into shares by means of a capital increase in kind within the authorized capital by a board decision of  march    the lenders will be offered the possibility to contribute their remaining receivables in share capital of the company on a next extraordinary shareholders’ meeting   shares and equity   the contribution of a total of eur  receivables under bridge and bond loans was executed at eur  per share which equals the  days average closing stock price before the day of the transaction for each new share eur  was accounted as new capital and eur  was booked as issue premium   as a result of the capital increase  new shares were created bringing the total number of shares subject to approval for listing on euronext from  today to  shares after listing   the capital of the company has been increased with eur  bringing the share capital of eur  before capital increase to eur  after capital increase a total of eur  is booked as premium issue   new funding   as part of the agreement most bondholders covering over  of the outstanding nominal value of the bond loans before transaction have agreed to participate in  mio eur of new funding for the company   these funds are structured as a new  years loan at  interest during the first year and  in the second year   going concern   with the current sales outlook for  and the renewed efforts of option’s stakeholders option will be able to execute its business plan for  in going concern   changes to the board and management   finally option announces changes to the board and management team as follows   qunova bvba represented by jan vorstermans has been replaced by crescemus bvba represented by mr pieter bourgeois optio